@staticmethod
def _merge_value(current, value):
    """Merge ``value`` into ``current`` when both represent nested dictionaries of features.

    Dictionaries (including nested :class:`Features`) are merged recursively key by key.
    A :class:`Sequence` whose ``feature`` is itself a dictionary is merged the same way.
    Otherwise ``value`` simply replaces ``current``.
